      <section>
        <title>Explosions in Brussels, safe haven soars in the markets</title>
        <chapter>
          <paragraph>
               The price of gold rose in conjunction with the news of the explosions in Brussels. The new terrorist
               attack in the heart of Europe is also reflected in the financial markets: equity markets treat
               weak, while the so-called "safe haven" undergoes a surge in value.</paragraph>
